 fresh mangoes The highly nutritious Mango is in season. It is rich in: magnesium and potassium, Vitamins A, C, K and can reduce blood levels. Mangoes can be made into a drink or added to one, a snack, dessert and even a meal. LAMB AND MANGO CURRY <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1725273 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="1280" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto.jpg 1500w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-598x598.jpg 598w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-1152x1152.jpg 1152w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-58x58.jpg 58w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-116x116.jpg 116w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-100x100.jpg 100w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-200x200.jpg 200w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-240x240.jpg 240w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-480x480.jpg 480w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Lamb-Coconut-Curry-With-Fresh-Mango-Chutney.-Photo-Gousto-600x600.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 1280px) 100vw, 1280px" /> INGREDIENTS METHOD Serve with rice and a glass of wine (optional). MANGO AND PASSION FRUIT FOOL <img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter wp-image-1725274 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2022/04/Mango-and-Passionfrurit-Fool.-Photo-The-Happy-Foodie.png